

== INSTALL ==
sudo apt update && sudo apt upgrade
apt install python3 pip3 git
git clone https://github.com/tebasdd/cgsw.git
pip3 install Flask


== RUN SERVER ==
python3 cgsw/swserver.py

== RUN FRONTEND ==
Open in webbrowser (i.e. the big display):
    http://<HOST>:8000/

Open in webbrowser (i.e. the remote control):
    http://<HOST>:8000/control

were <HOST> is 'localhost', the RasPi-IP, ...!
